These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Food: peas, carrot, garlic
1. Food:carrot is on the right of Food:garlic##1
2. Food:peas is on the far right##1
3. Food:peas is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Food   | garlic | carrot | peas |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
City: hamburg, paris, berlin
1. City:paris is in an odd position##4
2. City:hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | hamburg | berlin | paris |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Cigar: dannemann, havana, prince
1. Cigar:havana is in an even position##4
2. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Cigar:prince##3
3. Cigar:prince is on the right of Cigar:havana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Cigar   | dannemann | havana | prince |

 #################################
 
